{"tid":1380981,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"笨柒毅進佬  得不到分數 擸正牌猛開槍就係防暴","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:27:24.000Z","uid":47374,"like":484,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"4b566a53bfae12116557d89c51dec468f6ec0c8b","tid":1380981,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"笨柒毅進佬  得不到分數<br />\n擸正牌猛開槍就係防暴<br />\n乜思想你都無<br />\n你係隻Popo<br />\n<br />\n元朗地鐵 過百件狂徒喺度<br />\n推冧個大肚 班狗睇唔到<br />\n報案無狗聽 完全無到<br />\n成班狗只識扑暈細路<br />\n<br />\n你咁好  嚟茶餐廳更好<br />\n成條Team都試到<br />\n人人會為你鋪枱布<br />\n濃痰肉醬 送到<br />\n滲精炒蛋有質素<br />\n鳩屎檸水 歡迎狂啜 味道就最好<br />\n好 平時一哥著草<br />\n遺忘一班細佬<br />\n隨時割𥱊 偉聰爽到<br />\n平時吹慣冷氣 你企街被擺佈<br />\nCondom 靠兩萬銀做到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你世代"},{"pid":"69412ce91237f867270436a5c7161e8b0047e20a","tid":1380981,"uid":47374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"打多咗三隻字添"},{"pid":"7eb117920622bd0a90e78a8135896b2d92381a70","tid":1380981,"uid":86723,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837594a8b219ee38e905b4ca40b59e9f53c209cd","tid":1380981,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41157d4adefe981f9698cb7365dad31adacf06e","tid":1380981,"uid":65289,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"唱左出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e95b062ab1a9db9db92cea83fca641af265e131","tid":1380981,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"推跌個